data.description: Opportunity awaits at this private 1.3 acre lot in the sought after community of Stow. Contractors take notice! A little TLC and the equity is through the roof! Recent kitchen and bathroom updates include new cabinets and appliances and bathroom vanity. Hardwood floors through most of top floor. This large level lot includes oversized shed/garage approximately 12X20ft for your tools and toys or vehicle storage. Enjoy a cup of coffee on the 3 season porch overlooking large private lot. Bring your ideas and grab this chance to get yourself a home in time to enjoy the Spring. Come take a look! Limited showings outside of open house.  Sold as is.
